After installing this game and copying in the crack I was asked for a windows live account to be able to save games. I clicked to create a new one, then scrolled to the bottom of the page to find the 'local profile' option.  This allows game saving, though not achievements. No game key or internet connection required.  Thanks and hope this helps others
